                            <footer>I have a footer!</footer>
                        </div>
                        <div class="card">
                            <header>
                                <h2>A short heading</h2>
                            </header>
                            <div class="content">
                                <p>
                                    The idea of reaching the North Pole by means of balloons appears to have been entertained many
